2012年1月13日[[吉里巴斯|吉里巴斯]]舉行'''[[吉里巴斯總統|總統]]選舉'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.radioaustralianews.net.au/stories/201112/3400097.htm?desktop |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-19 |archive-date=2012-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120429220622/http://www.radioaustralianews.net.au/stories/201112/3400097.htm?desktop |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之前在2011年10月進行了[[2011年吉里巴斯議會選舉|兩輪議會選舉]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mherrera.org/elections.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-19 |archive-date=2011-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110526192300/http://www.mherrera.org/elections.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。時任總統[[湯安諾|湯安諾]]在是次選舉中尋求第3個四年任期<ref name=islandsbusiness>{{cite news|first=Robert|last=Matau|title=Tong confirms contesting next election|url=http://www.islandsbusiness.com/islands_business/index_dynamic/containerNameToReplace=MiddleMiddle/focusModuleID=19881/overideSkinName=issueArticle-full.tpl|work=Islands Business|publisher=|date=2011-10-12|accessdate=2011-10-17|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111020151806/http://www.islandsbusiness.com/islands_business/index_dynamic/containerNameToReplace%3DMiddleMiddle/focusModuleID%3D19881/overideSkinName%3DissueArticle-full.tpl|archivedate=2011-10-20}}</ref><ref name=rnzi2>{{cite news |first= |last= |title=Kiribati President confident he can win third term |url=http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read&id=63396 |work=Radio New Zealand International |publisher= |date=2011-09-27 |accessdate=2011-10-17 |archive-date=2010-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100924081452/http://www.rnzi.com/pages/news.php?op=read |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最後以42.18%得票率擊敗對手Tetaua Taitai及前聯合同盟黨黨主席[[瑞米塔·拜尼阿米纳|瑞米塔·拜尼阿米纳]]<ref name=eastwest/>。

本次大選原定2011年12月30日舉行，但為了讓民眾慶祝[[新年|新年]]，於是將選舉推遲至2012年1月13日<ref name=ann>{{cite news|first=|last=|title=Kiribati elections delayed|url=http://australianetworknews.com/stories/201112/3400097.htm?desktop|work=Australia News Network|publisher=|date=2011-12-30|accessdate=2012-01-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120701130852/http://australianetworknews.com/stories/201112/3400097.htm?desktop|archivedate=2012-07-01}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
根據《吉里巴斯憲法》的規定，每屆總統選舉的候選人均由議會選出，最多4個。總統一屆的任期是4年，最多可連任2次<ref name=eastwest/>。

== 候選人 ==
2011年改組的新議會提名3位候選人<ref name=eastwest>{{cite news |first= |last= |title=Parliament Nominates 3 Candidates for Kiribati President |url=http://pidp.eastwestcenter.org/pireport/2011/November/11-28-04.htm |work=The Kiribati Independent |publisher=East–West Center's Pacific Islands Report |date=2011-11-25 |accessdate=2012-01-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150212001741/http://pidp.eastwestcenter.org/pireport/2011/November/11-28-04.htm |archivedate=2015-02-12 }}</ref>：
* [[湯安諾|湯安諾]]－自2003年起擔任總統。
* Tetaua Taitai－醫生及政治人物。
* [[瑞米塔·拜尼阿米纳|瑞米塔·拜尼阿米纳]]－前聯合同盟黨黨主席。

